      <li><strong>Break the Wicker hold first.</strong> He chairs SASC. No markup, no floor. Constituent + VSO pressure in Mississippi is the primary lever. Media in MS markets is the secondary lever. The goal is a public commitment from Wicker to schedule committee action or an explanation of why he won't.</li>
